posting_body: ['Ideally Located Ballard Loft Studio Unit!', 'Property Address', '5403 Ballard Ave NW Unit 211 | Seattle, WA 98107-4014', 'Available:', '07/23/2022', 'Offered By', 'Lakeshore Corporation', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'Live comfortably in this incredible, large open LOFT studio unit with hardwood floors, exposed brick walls, common area bike storage and secured building entry!', 'Enjoy all that Downtown Ballard has to offer right outside your front door.', 'Get your morning espresso or tea from the in-building Caffe Umbria or Miro Tea and pamper yourself at Vain Salon.', 'Step outside the building to the conveniently located Majestic Bay Theaters, Olympic Athletic Club, and year round Farmers Market all just steps away!', 'SCHEDULE SHOWING @ https://showdigs.co/sMe56I', 'show contact info', '<URL>/', '<URL>/', '<URL>', '<URL>/', '<URL>/', '<URL>', 'Monthly Rent: $1895 + $75 flat monthly fee for W/S/G (+$25 for each additional occupant)', 'Deposit: $1000', 'Lease Term: 12 Months', 'Pets: Dogs only; $50 per month pet rent', 'Parking: City Street Parking Only', 'Tenant pays electric.', '*$49 non-refundable application fee per each applicant age 18 and older.', 'Key Words: Ballard, Downtown, Seattle, Ballard Ave NW, Lakeshore.', 'Amenities', 'Coin-Operated Laundry In Building', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Exposed Brick Walls', 'Common Area Bike Storage', 'Secured Building Entry', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 500', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,895.00', 'Available:', '07/23/2022', 'Application Fee: $49.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,000.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats not allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
